    "narrative": {
      "executive_summary": "Verdant Skincare delivered 8.0% organic click growth in July, driven by ranking improvements for educational content around sensitive skin and ingredient education. However, overall site sessions fell 2.3% and engagement dropped 7.2%, indicating a disconnect between search visibility gains and on-site conversion quality. AI visibility rose 5.1% with particularly strong 9.9% growth in Copilot, though share of voice slipped 4.7% as competitors maintained dominance. Revenue held flat at 47,906 GBP despite 2.9% fewer conversions, suggesting higher-value transactions but fragile momentum.",
      "highlights": [
